<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>디테일 화면 - 구독EASY</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/result.css" />
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="wrap container">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="logo">
                <a href="/"><img src="/images/logo.png"/></a>
            </h1>
            <from action="/search" method="GET">
                <div class="search">
                    <input placeholder="카테고리 검색" name="q" autocomplete="off"/>
                    <button class="searchBtn" type="submit">
                        <svg id="searchBtn" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <circle cx="17.5781" cy="17.5781" r="5.32812" stroke-width="2"></circle>
                            <path d="M21.6182 21.618L24.7501 24.75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </from>
        </div>
        <nav class="gnb">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="#" style="color: red; font-weight: bold">MY 구독</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">로그아웃</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>
<main>
    <section>
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="top-logo">
                    <img src="/images/netflix.png"/>
                </div>
                <div class="content-desc">
                    <li>서비스명</li>
                    <li>NETFLIX</li>
                </div>
                <div class="content-desc">
                    <li>카테고리</li>
                    <li>영화, 드라마</li>
                </div>
                <div class="content-desc">
                    <li>서비스 설명</li>
                    <li>각종 시리즈, 영화, 애니메이션, 다큐멘터리 등 다양한 콘텐츠를
                        여러 디바이스에서 시청할 수 있는 스트리밍 서비스</li>
                </div>
                <div class="content-desc">
                    <li>홈페이지</li>
                    <a href="#" target="_blank"><li>https://www.netflix.com/kr</li></a>
                </div>
                <div class="content-desc">
                    <li>가격 정책</li>
                    <li>9,500 원 ~ 17,000 원</li>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="middle">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="middle-word">
                <h2><strong>넷플릭스</strong>와 비슷한 다른 구독 서비스</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="middle-content">
                <ul class="grid">
                    <li class="content-box">
                        <img class="content-logo" src="/images/netflix.png"/>
                        <h4 class="content-name">넷플릭스</h4>
                        <p class="desc">영화, TV 프로그램 무제한 감상</p>
                        <a href="#">
                            <div class="detail">
                                가격비교/상세보기
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="content-box">
                        <img class="content-logo" src="/images/watcha.png"/>
                        <h4 class="content-name">왓챠</h4>
                        <p class="desc">영화, TV 프로그램 무제한 감상</p>
                        <a href="#">
                            <div class="detail">
                                가격비교/상세보기
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="content-box">
                        <img class="content-logo" src="/images/disney.png"/>
                        <h4 class="content-name">디즈니 플러스</h4>
                        <p class="desc">영화, TV 프로그램 무제한 감상</p>
                        <a href="#">
                            <div class="detail">
                                가격비교/상세보기
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
<footer>
    <div class="wrap">
        <p>Copyright © 2022 INHA University Project. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>